{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ddac3a4ab","title":"关于打招呼问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"157add3303","index":0,"year":1975,"month":11,"day":13,"articleId":"0ddac3a4ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"993375cfc6","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周荣鑫，当时任教育部部长。李昌，当时任中国科学院副院长。胡耀邦，当时任中国科学院党的核心小组负责人。"},{"id":"ad77da4e89","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"原文如此。据毛泽东的联络员毛远新1975年11月13日的记录，“胡”指国务院政治研究室主要负责人胡乔木。"},{"id":"0c3dc81ff7","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘冰，当时任清华大学党委副书记、革委会副主任。李井泉，原任中共中央西南局第一书记，当时任中共中央委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8211d0beff","type":"title","text":"关于打招呼问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab"},{"id":"993375cfc6","type":"paragraph","text":"过去只有河南同80%的县委书记打了招呼，所以没有受冲击。在多数人身上复杂一点。桃花源中人，不知有汉，何论魏普。要估计这种情况。一些老同志打个招呼，如周荣鑫、李昌、胡耀邦、胡、刘冰、李井泉等几十人也要打招呼","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab"}],"page":{"id":"0ff1b20149","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0ddac3a4ab","start":95,"end":95}}}},"__N_SSG":true}